snippet.title: Dead Ink Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1661600
Dead Ink is a souls-like game with a 3D printing twist, set at dizzying height atop a perilous vertical world. Discover printers and use harvested ink from your enemies to print weapons, inventory items and your corporeal form. https://offwidthgames.com
